  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/848660/extras/ceeed49af04dc52633568af9c086a806.webp?t=1601831142\" width=365 height=45 /></span><br><br>Cool Headed is a puzzle casual-programming game.<br>Combine and use your bots to reach the objective!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to play?</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/848660/extras/abf2d5a8e1a2db759936c9815b6d667a.avif?t=1601831142\" width=168 height=92 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pick a level on the overworld</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Compose your team<br></li><li>Give orders, tweak the timings<br></li><li>Deploy!<br></li><li>Try again...</li></ul><br>Win by having one bot reaching the objective.<br>Will you have the heart to sacrifice the rest of the team?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/848660/extras/eb3956d379e418fa1ad50b6136e9ca9e.webp?t=1601831142\" width=32 height=52 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>more then 110 level of progressive difficulty<br></li><li>bots with diverse abilities<br></li><li>no time pressure and unlimited tries<br></li><li>lots of secrets to uncover</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/848660/extras/688b852c360a41946812b1241ce7c045.webp?t=1601831142\" width=36 height=52 /></span> <strong>Good luck!</strong>",
